	<term>FBevel <emphasis remap='I'>None,Left,Right,Top, Bottom, NoOutline</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Defines 3D bevel of WinList buttons for windows that are in
        	focused state.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="Bevel#synopsis">Bevel flags</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
